        },
        {
            "title": "香港法院勒令中國房企景瑞控股清盤",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"香港法院勒令中國房企景瑞控股清盤\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vuV0ZX4heMZYwLzX39RHMw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-08/3d2a84d0-58e0-11ef-862d-c25a0f5cdbd9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">香港法院勒令中國房企景瑞控股清盤</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
